source.name: Fruit and Vegetable Market News Custom Search
source.description: The primary function of the Fruit and Vegetable  Market News Division of the Fruit and Vegetable Programs  is to provide an exchange of information for growers, shippers, wholesalers, researchers and others on supplies, demand and prices of fresh fruit and vegetables and speciality crops.
